Class ScrollingSmoother

java.lang.Object
  org.eclipse.nebula.animation.ScrollingSmoother

public class ScrollingSmoother
extends Object

Allows to replace the default scrolling behavior by an animation effect.

Compatible with :

  • Shell
  • StyledText
  • Canvas
  • Gallery

Author:
Nicolas Richeton
